  "detailed_description": [
    {
      "heading": "Reliable Cellular Connectivity",
      "text": "The Ubiquiti UMR-Industrial is a compact and ruggedized LTE Cat 4 mobile Wi-Fi router designed specifically for industrial and mission-critical IoT applications. Built to withstand harsh environments, it offers a reliable and versatile solution for connecting your industrial devices to the internet via cellular networks. This feature-rich router supports LTE Category 4, providing download speeds of up to 150 Mbps and upload speeds of up to 50 Mbps. Additionally, the UMR-Industrial boasts automatic failover functionality.  In case of a disruption in your primary connection (cellular, wired WAN, or Wi-Fi WAN), the router seamlessly switches to a backup option, ensuring uninterrupted data transmission for your critical applications."
    },
    {
      "heading": "Advanced Functionality",
      "text": "The Ubiquiti UMR-Industrial features two Gigabit Ethernet ports, one of which can function as a PoE output, allowing you to power compatible devices directly through the router (PoE+ input required for PoE passthrough).  The router also supports site-to-site VPN and VPN client routing, enabling secure communication between your industrial network and other locations. For added functionality, the UMR-Industrial incorporates an outdoor GPS receiver for location tracking. This feature can be valuable for applications where asset tracking or remote monitoring is required."
    },
    {
      "heading": "Versatile Power & Mounting",
      "text": "The Ubiquiti UMR-Industrial caters to various deployment scenarios with its versatile power options and mounting flexibility. The UMR-Industrial supports a variety of power sources, including UniFi PoE switches, USB Type-C, and 4-pin ATX DC power connectors, providing you with the flexibility to choose the most suitable power option for your specific needs. The router also offers flexible mounting options, including wall, pole, and DIN rail mounting, allowing for easy integration into various industrial settings."
    },
    {
      "heading": "Built for Harsh Environments",
      "text": "The Ubiquiti UMR-Industrial is built to endure harsh environments.  Its weatherproof enclosure with the included cover protects the internal components from dust, moisture, and extreme temperatures. External antennas for Mobile/LTE, GPS, and Wi-Fi connectivity further enhance its functionality and signal strength in outdoor locations.  With its reliable cellular connectivity, advanced networking features, and ruggedized design, the Ubiquiti UMR-Industrial is an ideal solution for deploying and managing industrial IoT applications in even the most demanding conditions."
    }
  ],
